title: 820-00850 Touch bar display image but wont react on touch
message:
Board got small liquid damage.
Display works fine on TB but wont respond on touch.
Liquid was near TB connector na d Touch ID (ID and power button works OK).

Found burned out component near TB connector - 
Any idea what is that?

title: 820-00850 Touch bar display image but wont react on touch
message:
Possibly filter cap.
Check continuity from its pads to nearest caps.
Short between pads?
